%208%201%207%2012%200%207%201%208%207%2010%2013%205%2023%2017%2023%2029v2h38v-5c2-7%204-14%208-18%204-5%2013-10%2017-10s3-2-2-12l-5-12H12m200%2033c-1%201-1%201%201%203%202%201%203%204%201%203-1-1-1%200-1%201%200%203%203%204%207%203%203-1%204%200%205%201%203%202%202%203-5%203l-7%202c-3%202%206%201%2011-1h6c1%201%202%200%201-3%200-2-1-3-2-3l-1-1-3-1-3-2-2-2-1-1-2-2h-5M3%20208c-2%200-2%203-2%2038%200%2042%200%2040%206%2037l7-3c3%200%203-1%203-4a5610%205610%200%2001-3-68H3m238%205l-1%202-1%201-2%201%201%201h1l-1%201c-1%200-2%200-3%202l-4%202-3%203-2%203-5%201-7%202-10-1-6-1-5-2-4-2-3-3-3-2c-3-3-5-2-5%204l-1%205-1%201-1%201c-1-1-3-3-6-11-2-5-5-8-5-6%200%203%208%2018%209%2017l1%201c-1%201%206%2012%2013%2018l14%2010%209%204%207-4%2011-8c5-3%2013-12%2016-17s5-13%203-10h-1v-2l-1-6c0-5%200-6-2-6l-2%201M94%20365l2%204%205%208c3%204%209%2012%2011%2012%201%200-1-7-4-11-4-7-14-16-14-13'%20fill='%2364ffda'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.0174418604651163,"src":"/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/ea4ab/profile_photo.jpg","srcSet":"/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/477ba/profile_photo.jpg 175w,\n/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/06776/profile_photo.jpg 350w,\n/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/ea4ab/profile_photo.jpg 700w,\n/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/91c9c/profile_photo.jpg 724w","srcWebp":"/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/89afa/profile_photo.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/9fca7/profile_photo.webp 175w,\n/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/37a4e/profile_photo.webp 350w,\n/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/89afa/profile_photo.webp 700w,\n/static/93f4f99acd368975f90c8fedd70e3c1a/0d437/profile_photo.webp 724w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"skills":["Java","Python","MySQL","RabbitMQ","Redis","React.js"]},"html":"<p>Hello! I'm Akash, a software engineer based in Bangalore.</p>\n<p>I love solving challenging problems, and wandering out of my comfort zone.</p>\n<!-- I enjoy creating things that live on the internet, whether that be websites, applications, or anything in between. My goal is to always build products that provide pixel-perfect, performant experiences. -->\n<p>After graduating from <a href=\"https://www.nitk.ac.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">National Institute of Technology Karnataka</a>, I joined the engineering team at <a href=\"https://www.myntra.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Myntra</a> where I work on a wide variety of interesting and meaningful projects on a daily basis.</p>\n<p>Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Senior Software Engineer","company":"Myntra","location":"Bangalore, India","navbar":"Myntra","range":"July 2017 - Present","url":"https://www.myntra.com/"},"html":"<!-- - Write modern, performant, maintainable code for a diverse array of client and internal projects\n- Work with a variety of different languages, platforms, frameworks, and content management systems such as JavaScript, TypeScript, Gatsby, React, Craft, Wordpress, Prismic, and Netlify\n- Communicate with multi-disciplinary teams of engineers, designers, producers, and clients on a daily basis -->\n<ul>\n<li>Full Stack Developer as part of the Supply Chain Inbound team, which focussed on building a platform from scratch, scaling to procure 500,000+ styles.</li>\n<li>Individually developed the Central Curation Engine end to end. This system helped curate styles on Myntra, garnering higher traffic positivity coming mainly from much lower brokenness â€”200k additional sessions.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Developed Replenishment Planner, which automated the inward flow for Top Selling Styles, which reduced TAT for Purchase Order generation to under 10 minutes.</p>\n<!-- - Designed an automated grading module, to add a layer of intelligence while making key decisions on inwards using Visenze API, to grade new styles based on image similarity. -->\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Key developer for Myntra Financial Planner, a financial planning tool tailored to the fashion e-commerce world. Here are some of my major contributions :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed data pipeline issues, and made it robust.</li>\n<li>Optimized reads in scenario approval flow, to make it 12x faster.</li>\n<li>Integrated Redis to cache aggregations, which improved performance of historic flows by 40%.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Redesigned the export feature, to minimize heap memory use by 80%.</p>\n<!-- - Worked with a variety of different languages and technologies such as Java, RabbitMQ, Redis, MySQL and ReactJs -->\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Software Engineering Intern","company":"Myntra","location":"Bangalore, India","navbar":"Myntra (Internship)","range":"May - July 2016","url":"https://www.myntra.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Developed a Machine Learning model using the K-means and K-prototype clustering algorithms, to build Size profiles based on the order/return history of each user. These profiles are used for size recommendation, enhancing the user's shopping experience.</li>\n<li>This helped minimize the returns in Myntra, reducing resources wasted on returns.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Research Intern","company":"Indian Institute of Science (IISc)","location":"Bangalore, India","navbar":"IISc","range":"May - July 2015","url":"https://www.iisc.ac.in/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Interned under the guidance of Prof. Y Narahari, Chairman, Dept of Computer Science &#x26; Automation at Indian Institute of Science (IISc).</li>\n<li>Worked on studying the effect of introducing a referral bonus in a crowdsource web-based auction system. Worked on running simulations of Vickrey Autctions on underlying social networks to understand the cause and effect of various parameters correlating to the success of the auction.</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"AlgoRaiding","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='250'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20250'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M152%20235v2c0%202%201%202%2012%202h11v-5h-11l-12%201'%20fill='%2364ffda'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.6055045871559632,"src":"/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/60290/renko.png","srcSet":"/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/847ef/renko.png 175w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/91cba/renko.png 350w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/60290/renko.png 700w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/f5f50/renko.png 1050w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/38674/renko.png 1400w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/949c2/renko.png 2880w","srcWebp":"/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/89afa/renko.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/9fca7/renko.webp 175w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/37a4e/renko.webp 350w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/89afa/renko.webp 700w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/78e7a/renko.webp 1050w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/03d34/renko.webp 1400w,\n/static/d5e79ffc074ea0ff3f144d17fae1f996/5c931/renko.webp 2880w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"tech":["Python","Algorithmic Trading","Renko"],"github":"https://github.com/akash-suresh/algo-raiding","external":null},"html":"<p>Developed a algorithmic trading script, which leverages the volatility of the stock market to make trades automatically, to make marginal profits and minimize loss using Renko charts.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"ChainRank","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='257'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20257'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M58%2071v6h-9v67c0%2063%200%2067-2%2067a9691%209691%200%200026