rio approval flow, to make it 12x faster.\n  - Integrated Redis to cache aggregations, which improved performance of historic flows by 40%.\n  - Redesigned the export feature, to minimize heap memory use by 80%. -->"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Replenishment Planner","tech":["Java","MySQL","RabbitMQ"],"github":"","external":""},"html":"<p>Part of the team that developed Replenishment Planner, which automated the inward flow for Top Selling Styles on <a href=\"https://www.myntra.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Myntra</a>, which reduced the TAT for Purchase Order generation to under 10 minutes.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Central Curation Engine","tech":["Java","MySQL","React.js"],"github":"","external":""},"html":"<p>Individually developed curation engine end to end. This system helped curate styles on <a href=\"www.myntra.com\">Myntra</a>, garnering higher traffic positivity coming mainly from much lower brokenness ~200k additional sessions.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Size Recommendation Engine","tech":["Python"],"github":"","external":""},"html":"<p>Developed a Machine Learning model using the K-means and K-prototype clustering algorithms, to build Size profiles based on the order/return history of each user. These profiles are used for size recommendation, enhancing the user's shopping experience.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Crowdsourced referral auctions","tech":["Python"],"github":"","external":""},"html":"<p>Studying the effect of introducting a referral bonus, in a crowdsourced web-based auction system. Worked on running simulations on social networks to understand the cause and effect of various parameters correlating to the success of the auction.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"FileTorrent","tech":["Java"],"github":"https://github.com/akash-suresh/filebus","external":""},"html":"<p>Developed an offline peer to peer networking software allowing users to share files through the network using overlay networks and multi-cast sockets in Java.</p>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Get In Touch","buttonText":"Say Hello"},"html":"<p>Although I'm not currently looking for any new opportunities, my inbox is always open. Whether you have a question or just want to say hi, I'll try my best to get back to you!</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{}}}